These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, romance
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, car
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | romance |
| Transport     | car | bus  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, soccer
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | kale      | blueberry         |
| Sport   | rugby | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, corn
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola   |
| Food       | corn  | pomegranate |

 #################################

 
